# Display constraints (non-negotiable)

DOKI is phone-only, portrait-only, single-viewport.

- **Portrait-locked.** No landscape. No rotation handling. Lock orientation in app.json/Expo config.
- **No scrolling.** Every screen fits in one viewport. No ScrollView on core screens. Roster may use paginated swipe (not vertical scroll).
- **No pinch-to-zoom.** Fixed-scale content. No zoom gestures.
- **Full-screen, edge-to-edge.** SafeAreaView for notch/dynamic island, fill the rest.
- **Responsive sizing.** iPhone SE (375×667pt) minimum, iPhone 15 Pro Max (430×932pt) maximum. Use percentage-based positioning. All pixel sizes in the spec are reference values for 390pt width — scale proportionally.
- **No tab bar / bottom nav.** Navigation via Home screen action grid + contextual back buttons.

If any code introduces ScrollView, horizontal orientation, pinch zoom, or a bottom tab navigator on a core game screen, it violates the spec.
